name: Skydiving
description:
Accept the challenge of the craziest jump race in history.

Overcome 10 jumps to win the cup and be the best SKY DIVING

Avoid the other participants. You only have five helmets.

Press space to expand your parachute before the time reaches zero.

Accumulate as little time as possible if you want to access both last jumps.
